财务部要求
根据提供的Excel，以TranID为KEY进行删除。
删除时候可能会有CMLEDGAPPLY关联，需要先删除关联数据
delete from cmledgapply where tranid = '0073895203'
delete from TB_CM_LEDGTOJRNL where tranid = '0073895203'
delete from cmledg where tranid = '0073895203'
